text: II I give, devise and bequeath all my property, real, personal and mixed, of whatever kind and nature and wheresoever situated, including but not limited to my one acre tract of land with dwelling, deed to which being recorded in Book 64, page 355, Register's Office of Lauderdale County, Tennessee, to my daughter, [Person-2] of Gates, Tennessee.
